---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { t } from "../../i18n/ui";

const lang = "en";
---

<Layout
    title={t(lang, "nav.datenschutz")}
    lang="en"
    description="Privacy Policy of Jannik Menzel: Information about the handling of personal data on this website."
    keywords="Privacy, Privacy Policy, Jannik Menzel, Data, GDPR, Website"
    og={{
        title: `${t(lang, "nav.datenschutz")} – Jannik Menzel`,
        description:
            "Privacy Policy of Jannik Menzel: Information about the handling of personal data on this website.",
        url: "https://jannikmenzel.me/en/datenschutz",
        image: "https://jannikmenzel.me/social-preview.png",
    }}
    twitter={{
        title: `${t(lang, "nav.datenschutz")} – Jannik Menzel`,
        description:
            "Privacy Policy of Jannik Menzel: Information about the handling of personal data on this website.",
        image: "https://jannikmenzel.me/social-preview.png",
    }}
    canonical="https://jannikmenzel.me/en/datenschutz"
>
    <main class="w-full container px-4 sm:px-16 mb-22" style="max-width: 1100px;">
        <!-- Header -->
        <header class="pt-20">
            <h1 class="text-center text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold font-display mb-4">
                {t(lang, "nav.datenschutz")}
            </h1>
            <div class="h-1 w-24 bg-primary mx-auto"></div>
        </header>

        <!-- Content -->
        <section class="mb-6 sm:mb-6 pt-22">
            <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-medium mb-2 flex justify-between items-baseline">
                <span>Introduction</span>
                <span class="text-base font-thin">Status: 03.04.2026</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="font-thin text-justify" style="hyphens: auto;">
                This privacy policy informs you about the type, scope and purpose of the processing
                of personal data (hereinafter "data") within my online offer and the associated
                websites, functions and content as well as external online presences, such as my
                social media profile.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-6 sm:mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-medium mb-2">Privacy at a Glance</h2>
            <p class="font-thin text-justify" style="hyphens: auto;">
                Here you will find a brief overview of what happens to your personal data when you
                visit this website. Personal data is any data that can be used to personally
                identify you.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section class="mb-6 sm:mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-medium mb-2">Who is responsible?</h2>
            <p class="font-thin text-justify" style="hyphens: auto;">
                The data processing on this website is carried out by me as the operator. You can
                find the contact details in the imprint.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section class="mb-6 sm:mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-medium mb-2">How is data collected?</h2>
            <p class="font-thin text-justify" style="hyphens: auto;">
                On the one hand, your data is collected by you providing it to me (e.g., via the
                contact form). Other data is collected automatically by the hosting provider when
                you visit the website (e.g., technical data such as browser, operating system, time
                of page request).
            </p>
        </section>
        <section class="mb-6 sm:mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-medium mb-2">What is the data used for?</h2>
            <p class="font-thin text-justify" style="hyphens: auto;">
                Part of the data is collected to ensure the website functions without errors. Other
                data may be used to analyze usage, although no external analysis tools are used on
                this site.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-6 sm:mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-medium mb-2">Purpose of Processing</h2>
            <p class="font-thin text-justify" style="hyphens: auto;">
                Processing is carried out to answer contact inquiries, to conduct pre-contractual
                measures, to provide my content, and to safeguard legitimate interests (e.g.,
                security and operation of the website).
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-6 sm:mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-medium mb-2">Contact Form</h2>
            <p class="font-thin text-justify" style="hyphens: auto;">
                If you contact me via the contact form, the data you enter (e.g., name, email
                address, message) will be processed for the purpose of handling your request and for
                possible follow-up questions. Processing is based on your consent or to fulfill a
                request (Art. 6 Para. 1 lit. a and b GDPR).
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-6 sm:mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-medium mb-2">
                Hosting, Server Logs and Technical Data
            </h2>
            <p class="font-thin text-justify" style="hyphens: auto;">
                The pages are operated by an external service provider (hosting provider). Each time
                the website is accessed, data is automatically collected in server log files, e.g.,
                IP address, time of server request, referrer URL, browser used, and possibly
                accessed pages. This data is technically required to ensure stability and security
                of the page.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-6 sm:mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-medium mb-2">Cookies</h2>
            <p class="font-thin text-justify" style="hyphens: auto;">
                This website partially uses so-called cookies. Cookies are small text files that are
                stored locally. They are used to make my offer more user-friendly, effective and
                secure. You can prevent the storage of cookies via your browser settings; in this
                case, parts of the website may be functionally restricted.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-6 sm:mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-medium mb-2">Analysis and Tracking Tools</h2>
            <p class="font-thin text-justify" style="hyphens: auto;">
                No analysis or tracking tools such as Google Analytics are used on this website.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-6 sm:mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-medium mb-2">Data Sharing</h2>
            <p class="font-thin text-justify" style="hyphens: auto;">
                Personal data is only shared with third parties if this is necessary for contract
                execution, I am legally obligated, or you have expressly consented.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-6 sm:mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-medium mb-2">Your Rights</h2>
            <p class="font-thin text-justify" style="hyphens: auto;">
                You have the right to information, correction, deletion, and restriction of the
                processing of your data. Furthermore, you can revoke consent given at any time and
                file a complaint with a supervisory authority.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-6 sm:mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-medium mb-2">Security</h2>
            <p class="font-thin text-justify" style="hyphens: auto;">
                I use technical and organizational security measures to protect your data against
                manipulation, loss, destruction, or unauthorized access by third parties.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-6 sm:mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-medium mb-2">Changes to this Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p class="font-thin text-justify" style="hyphens: auto;">
                I reserve the right to adapt this privacy policy if necessary. The current version
                will be published on this page.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-lightOff">
            <p class="text-justify" style="hyphens: auto;">
                For privacy-related questions, please use the contact form on the website or write
                an email to the address provided above.
            </p>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
